{"tid":1005918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲史上最熱一月山火頻生　美英法遭遇嚴寒","createTime":"2019-02-02T14:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T14:31:42.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64f409d95f4eafc487f1a11fadf36dbf9b61f628","tid":1005918,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"2019年才過了一個月，但全球多地卻接連出現極端天氣。「極地渦旋」（Polar Vortex）導致美國部分地區極度嚴寒，錄得零下54度；英國蘇格蘭錄得零下14.4度；法國部分地方因大雪而發出天氣警告。另一邊廂，澳洲則錄得有紀錄以來的「最熱1月」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國：寒冷天氣造成至少17人死亡，超過2300班航班取消，11個州份周四（1月31日）氣溫比位於北極圈北部的阿拉斯加州城市烏特恰維克（Utqiagvik）更低。在芝加哥的醫院，至今為50名凍傷病人診治，部分人或需截肢。<br />\n<br />\n英國：蘇格蘭布雷馬（Braemar）周四錄得零下14.4度，是英國自2012年以後最低氣溫紀錄。倫敦希斯路機場周五（1日）部分航班取消，同日英格蘭和威爾斯數以百計學校關閉。<br />\n<br />\n法國：本周初期出現大雪，國家氣象部門發出天氣警告。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲：錄得史上最熱的1月。北部地區一處乾涸水坑發現大約40具馬屍。新南威爾斯和昆士蘭省大量狐蝠死亡。塔斯曼尼亞州發生多場叢林大火，數百名消防員出動才能控制火勢。<br />\n<br />\n（美國有線新聞網絡）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190202/s00005/1549080162450/%e3%80%90%e6%a5%b5%e7%ab%af%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%a3-%e5%a4%9a%e5%9c%96%e3%80%91%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e5%8f%b2%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%80%e7%86%b1%e4%b8%80%e6%9c%88%e5%b1%b1%e7%81%ab%e9%a0%bb%e7%94%9f-%e7%be%8e%e8%8b%b1%e6%b3%95%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87%e5%9a%b4%e5%af%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190202%2Fs00005%2F1549080162450%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25a5%25b5%25e7%25ab%25af%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e6%25b0%25a3-%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%259c%2596%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e5%258f%25b2%25e4%25b8%258a%25e6%259c%2580%25e7%2586%25b1%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%25b1%25b1%25e7%2581%25ab%25e9%25a0%25bb%25e7%2594%259f-%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%258b%25b1%25e6%25b3%2595%25e9%2581%25ad%25e9%2581%2587%25e5%259a%25b4%25e5%25af%2592&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2dUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=a845cda4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190202%2Fs00005%2F1549080162450%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25a5%25b5%25e7%25ab%25af%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e6%25b0%25a3-%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%259c%2596%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e5%258f%25b2%25e4%25b8%258a%25e6%259c%2580%25e7%2586%25b1%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%25b1%25b1%25e7%2581%25ab%25e9%25a0%25bb%25e7%2594%259f-%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%258b%25b1%25e6%25b3%2595%25e9%2581%25ad%25e9%2581%2587%25e5%259a%25b4%25e5%25af%2592&h=515c5c61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190202/s00005/1549080162450/%e3%80%90%e6%a5%b5%e7%ab%af%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%a3-%e5%a4%9a%e5%9c%96%e3%80%91%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e5%8f%b2%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%80%e7%86%b1%e4%b8%80%e6%9c%88%e5%b1%b1%e7%81%ab%e9%a0%bb%e7%94%9f-%e7%be%8e%e8%8b%b1%e6%b3%95%e9%81%ad%e9%81%87%e5%9a%b4%e5%af%92</a>"},{"pid":"8e717bb08319ea4c8b16897a619ad6f1eaad9b73","tid":1005918,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"到底係咪全球暖化咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0e5602430956c0279c048022ec2d2f1be23e95","tid":1005918,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}